Usage: violationBrowserDeleteByArea [-help] [-all] [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-all                    # Deletes markers from the entire design area.
                        # (bool, optional)
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Specifies the area from which to delete markers.
                        # (string, optional)